name: Yadee Solutions
product_desc:
Djaamyadee is an application available in web, mobile and USSD version contributing to digitalizing the transport sector for better mobility and sustainable development in the african continent. 
Our app helps its users to find the means of transport of their wish, to transport parcels inside and outside the country, to save time and to pay their transport costs without moving.
Its added value is that in addition to its ease of use, the solution is available via a menu USSD allowing accessibility on a large scale especially in case of problem of internet connection which is a big concern in Africa.
high_concept: We revolutionize transportation through new technologies
markets: Telecommunications, Mobile Payments, Mobile Application, Logistics / Transportation / Shipping

name: myAgro
product_desc: In the long-term, myAgro envisions its model for change spurring structural shifts in two arenas: how governments and multilaterals fund the agricultural sector, and how the financial inclusion sector provides services to smallholder farmers. When myAgro can demonstrate the power of mobile layaway to serve farmers and the bottom of the pyramid, there will be a major disruption in traditional antipoverty strategies for the sector at large. When financing is self-directed from smallholder farmers themselves, it is, by definition, sustainable. The market will react to this unlocked capital by providing better and more useful services or products.
markets: Mobile Enterprise, Agriculture, International Development, Social Enterprise
